# Third-party dependencies are declared here for forward reference but are NOT
# added as live submodules during Phase 0 — the no-op stub targets link none of
# them, keeping the CI build fast. Each later phase adds the submodule it needs:
#
#   Phase 3 (DSP):     spdlog, kissfft
#   Phase 4 (UI):      JUCE
#   Phase 6 (Voice):   rnnoise
#   IPC backbone:      flatbuffers
#
# To populate one, run e.g.:
#   git submodule add https://github.com/juce-framework/JUCE.git           third_party/JUCE
#   git submodule add https://github.com/xiph/rnnoise.git                  third_party/rnnoise
#   git submodule add https://github.com/gabime/spdlog.git                 third_party/spdlog
#   git submodule add https://github.com/google/flatbuffers.git            third_party/flatbuffers
#   git submodule add https://github.com/mborgerding/kissfft.git           third_party/kissfft
#
# and pin a tag, then add the matching entry below.
[submodule "third_party/spdlog"]
	path = third_party/spdlog
	url = https://github.com/gabime/spdlog
